						<p>Vijayanagara, Bhūpati-Uḍaiyar, Hēviḷambi, Tai 8 = A.D. 1418, January 3.</p>						

						<p>Much worn out. This registers a peace settlement between two groups of <hi rend="italic">kaṇmāḷar</hi> who were quarrelling with each other resulting in some murder.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">IPS</hi>, No. 697, lines 1—6.]</p>						

